{"tid":207362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無J香味既巴絲","createTime":"2017-04-19T00:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T00:09:58.000Z","uid":100432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e389af93a5cc710769a6956175d54266cb46846","tid":207362,"uid":100432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"好撚鐘意聞極小部份人既汗味 體香 髮香<br />\n仲有去惠康啲洗衣粉同紙巾味 世界級享受來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過唔會好明顯咁控埋去猛索 最多都係係隔離偷偷地呼吸下就好滿足<br />\n<br />\n希望我唔算變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f77d5097994e2039b955384501c5599335bba18","tid":207362,"uid":100757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"髮香控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6ca3c154d0bf35187bd74390c909f805bae1da","tid":207362,"uid":100432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>髮香控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解通常都係女仔香啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係有一次玩誠實與大膽果類野 要簡三個人<br />\n聞佢地頭頂最中間果個位<br />\n我發現男仔個頭反而正中間好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}